---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Project Alpha | Dar1an" description="企业级 Web 设计系统">
  <article class="project-detail">
    <header class="project-header">
      <span class="project-category">Design System</span>
      <h1 class="project-title">
        <span class="en">Project Alpha</span>
        <span class="cn">企业级 Web 设计系统</span>
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="project-image-full">
      <img src="https://img.dar1an.dpdns.org/Picgo/2025/10-29-18-31-57.jpg" alt="Project Alpha" />
    </div>

    <div class="project-content">
      <section class="project-section">
        <h2>项目概述</h2>
        <p>Project Alpha 是一个面向企业级应用的 Web 设计系统。它包含了完整的组件库、设计规范和开发指南，帮助团队快速构建一致性的用户界面。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <h2>设计目标</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>建立统一的设计语言和视觉规范</li>
          <li>提高开发效率，减少重复工作</li>
          <li>确保跨产品的一致用户体验</li>
          <li>支持快速迭代和扩展</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="project-section">
        <h2>技术栈</h2>
        <p>Figma, React, TypeScript, Storybook, TailwindCSS</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="project-footer">
      <a href="/portfolio/" class="back-link">
        ← <span class="en">Back to Portfolio</span>
        <span class="cn">返回作品集</span>
      </a>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .project-detail {
    padding: 120px 10% 50px;
    padding-left: 140px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .project-header {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .project-category {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-top: 15px;
  }

  .project-title .cn {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .project-image-full {
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .project-image-full img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  .project-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .project-section {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .project-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .project-section p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .project-section ul {
    margin-left: 20px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 2;
  }

  .project-footer {
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .back-link .cn {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-detail {
      padding: 100px 5% 100px;
    }

    .project-title {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
